&lt;li&gt;Drive sales of Workhelix products, leveraging industry knowledge to position our solutions effectively.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally with product, marketing, and operations teams to shape go-to-market strategies and influence product development based on customer feedback.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build trust with enterprise clients and create long-term, value-driven relationships.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work backwards from customer needs to design innovative solutions that address their most critical challenges.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
